### Create book
POST {{host}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Old Man and the Sea",
  "isbn": "978-0684801223",
  "publishedDate": "1952-09-01",
  "genre": "Fiction",
  "authorId": "{{authorId}}"
}

### List books (pagination)
GET {{host}}/books?page=1&limit=10

### Search books
GET {{host}}/books?search=Sea&page=1&limit=10

### List books by author
GET {{host}}/books?authorId={{authorId}}&page=1&limit=10

### Get book by id
GET {{host}}/books/{{bookId}}

### Update book
PATCH {{host}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Old Man and the Sea (Revised Edition)",
  "genre": "Classic Fiction"
}

### Delete book
DELETE {{host}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

# Notes:
# - Replace {{authorId}} and {{bookId}} with real IDs from API responses.
# - Use the Signin request in auth.http to obtain tokens, then paste the token into @accessToken.